<br>
My best suggestion is, cast less.  I found as a Troll SHD soloing, that I was better off saving some mana and tanking some instead.  Since I regen rather quickly, It made more sense to have to sit and regain 2 bubs each of health/mana instead of waiting twice as long to regen 4 bubs of mana and no health.   <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub12.ezboard.com/uranoon.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ranoon</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 9<br> <font color=#6FB8DD>(8/26/01 1:45 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub40.ezboard.com/fthesaryrntavernclassdiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=174.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Hybrid help with mana regen</span><hr size=1> /doh<br>
